time_low":141.55,"long_business_summary":"Hindoostan Mills Limited manufactures and sells textile products in India and internationally. It operates through two segments, Textile and Engineering. The company offers open end yarns; and greige and processed fabrics. It also offers refiling of elastic calendar bowls, calendaring machines, squeeze rolls, and related products for the textile, paper, and steel industries. In addition, the company offers cotton/comber, polyamide, wool paper, hard chrome, laxmi helextra, ECK NCCM, flax paper, and design roll, as well as wiper bar. It also exports its products. The company was formerly known as Sirdar Carbonic Gas Company Ltd. and changed its name to Hindoostan Mills Limited in May 2011. Hindoostan Mills Limited was founded in 1873 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}